				<table width="100%" cellspacing="0">
				<tr>
				
					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Asunto:</b> Tres tipos de líderes y liderazgo</div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=3460&amp;sid=e7a729da80a1883894fd8c928f7872c7#p3460"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Nota" title="Nota" /></a><b>Publicado:</b> Mié Mar 15, 2006 11:00 pm&nbsp;</div></td>
